      "message": "💡 Big ambition — love it! That's a long-term goal worth working towards. For this exercise, can you describe a smaller version you could start with limited time and money right now? The skills you learn here will help you build towards the bigger dream.",
      "socratic_hint": "The student has described a very ambitious, long-term goal — encourage it! Ask: what is the smallest version of this idea you could start today with no budget? Learning business fundamentals on a small scale first is exactly how the founders of big companies got started."
